      </svg><input type="text" id="search-input" placeholder="Cari nama dosen atau mata kuliah..." class="w-full pl-12 pr-4 py-3 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 focus:border-indigo-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-100 outline-none transition-all text-slate-700 placeholder-slate-400">
